34:17.190 --> 34:17.989
Terima kasih.

34:18.110 --> 34:19.250
Baiklah, hati-hati.

34:19.250 --> 34:19.840
Jumpa lagi.

34:19.840 --> 34:20.590
Jumpa lagi.

34:43.040 --> 34:43.780
Macam mana?

34:45.699 --> 34:46.630
Saya dah tua begini

34:46.630 --> 34:47.710
